7.html|accessdate=|author=王菁珩|date=|format=|publisher=《[[炎黄春秋|炎黄春秋]]》|language=zh|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714221024/http://www.yhcqw.com/36/9207.html|archivedate=2020-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=文革对中国核基地的损害：4000人被审查 40人自尽|url=http://news.ifeng.com/history/zhongguoxiandaishi/detail_2012_05/02/14277600_0.shtml|author=王菁珩|date=2012-05-02|work=[[凤凰网|凤凰网]]|publisher=《[[炎黄春秋|炎黄春秋]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024223417/http://news.ifeng.com/history/zhongguoxiandaishi/detail_2012_05/02/14277600_0.shtml|archive-date=2019-10-24|dead-url=yes|access-date=2019-10-31}}</ref>。1968年，“[[两弹一星|两弹一星]]元勋”[[姚桐斌|姚桐斌]]被毒打致死、“两弹一星元勋”[[赵九章|赵九章]]自杀身亡，而“两弹一星元勋”[[郭永怀|郭永怀]]于1968年不幸空难逝世后，其太太[[李佩|李佩]]（中国语言学家）被隔离审查、自杀未遂<ref name=":4" /><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=周恩来与中央专门委员会|url=http://zhouenlai.people.cn/n1/2018/0528/c409117-30018296.html|author=杨明伟|date=2018-05-28|publisher=[[人民网|人民网]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024215605/http://zhouenlai.people.cn/n1/2018/0528/c409117-30018296.html|archive-date=2019-10-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=文革惨案之赵九章之死|url=http://renwu99.info/node/2971|date=2014-08-11|publisher=传奇人物网|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024220242/http://renwu99.info/node/2971|archive-date=2019-10-24|dead-url=yes|access-date=2019-10-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=我国著名语言学家、国科大教授李佩先生逝世|url=http://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2017/1/365685.shtm|author=|date=2017-01-12|format=|work=|publisher=[[科学网|科学网]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609012257/http://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2017/1/365685.shtm|archive-date=2019-06-09|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-10-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=李佩在郭永怀遇难前后的遭遇——李佩文革经历考|url=http://hua-xinmin.hxwk.org/2017/02/22/%e6%9d%8e%e4%bd%a9%e5%9c%a8%e9%83%ad%e6%b0%b8%e6%80%80%e9%81%87%e9%9a%be%e5%89%8d%e5%90%8e%e7%9a%84%e9%81%ad%e9%81%87-%e6%9d%8e%e4%bd%a9%e6%96%87%e9%9d%a9%e7%bb%8f%e5%